{"tid":839152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡移民官員被控收受中國女子性賄賂","createTime":"2018-09-27T16:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T08:46:37.000Z","uid":184679,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a4b04c350dde44f5ca0278d47d060c237018cb1d","tid":839152,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T16:59:07.000Z","msg":"一名新加坡移民官員涉嫌收受至少2名中國女子性賄賂，作為協助她們延長特別准證的「酬勞」，這名移民官員今天遭到指控，在這個素以清廉形象聞名的城市國家十分罕見。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡移民與關卡局官員陳鵬山（Chin Peng Sum，譯音）同時被控將當局即將突襲檢查的消息通風報信給這2名女子，並刪除彼此之間可當成犯罪證據的簡訊而被控妨礙司法公正。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡貪汙調查局表示，51歲的警曹長陳鵬山被控收受外國女子性賄賂，這些女子藉此換取特別准證延長。<br />\n<br />\n貪汙調查局表示，陳鵬山也因事先向2女通風報信協助她們躲避查緝，被控違反政府機密法。<br />\n<br />\n貪汙調查局表示，公務人員追求一己私利，利用職務貪汙牟利，屬嚴重違法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2564113\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2564113&d=%2BoX3ALZ8q%2FvQFAm0m5BtCDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=4dfd533c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2564113&h=ad45b336\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2564113</a>"},{"pid":"e0fb6fb12051521ae46dabf7bafebf6664fd3ecd","tid":839152,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T01:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6f0c04ceaf34dc80afa34594b26eb867cf1f41","tid":839152,"uid":29093,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T01:04:22.000Z","msg":"當年通過一日150.名額條友應該成世可享屌免費蝗雞？"},{"pid":"c45034418b1da89641ffd8a64344a06c9d175d2b","tid":839152,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a6f0c04ceaf34dc80afa34594b26eb867cf1f41","tid":839152,"uid":29093,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T01:04:22.000Z","msg":"當年通過一日150.名額條友應該成世可享屌免費蝗雞？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T02:20:09.000Z","msg":"哇 咁班廢老未變哂潛在綠帽"},{"pid":"0e0f747d4e2e9ce